title: Gitshock DAO
text: Gitshock DAO is a community driven governance which aim to support the mission of Gitshock Finance, to provide a suitable network where everyone, including enterprise and SMEs can adopt crypto easier than before. Gitshock DAO will be by Gitshock Labs and aim to involve various global web3 societies
